title: [Yugreckol's General Store]
[Yugreckol's Outfitting]
[Yugreckol's Magic Shoppe]
description: A tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls, and an uneven wooden ceiling rises overhead.  A worn rug sits in one corner of an unfinished wooden floor.  There is an ora-bound large walnut trunk on one side of the shop and a large oak table on the other.
